See Sequence Diagram in Section 5.5 of the main proposal.

B.5 Energy Management Subsystem

The phone’s energy manager uses a state machine with states:

· Standalone Satellite – high power, used when vehicle not present.
· Relay Active – satellite transceiver off, only local Wi‑Fi active.
· Charging – wireless charging from vehicle.
· Solar Trickle – if integrated solar cell provides > 0.5 W.

The state transition is controlled by the AI optimization layer, which minimises energy consumption while ensuring user‑perceived connectivity.

